<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<%- include head.ejs %>
<script type='text/javascript' src='/scripts/entry.js'></script>
<body>
    <%- include navbar.ejs %>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col s3">
            <ul class="tabs no-tabs-css">
                <li class="no-tab-css row tab ">
                    <a class="block center card blue-grey darken-1">
                        <div class="card-content white-text">
                            <i class="material-icons">flash_on</i>
                            <p>The Status Quo</p>
                            <p class="light center">
                                Public transportation is stuck in an archaic era. In the age of the internet, things are still decided upon and scheduled manually, and vehicles' locations not tracked.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="no-tab-css row tab ">
                    <a class="block center card blue-grey darken-1">
                        <div class="card-content white-text">
                            <i class="material-icons">polymer</i>
                            <p>Enter Falcon</p>
                            <p class="light center">
                                Falcon presents an ecosystem wherein the latency, costs, and mishaps are greatly reduced through systematic elimination of manual work and human error.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="no-tab-css row tab ">
                    <a class="block center card blue-grey darken-1">
                        <div class="card-content white-text">
                            <i class="material-icons">account_circle</i>
                            <p>On the Shoulders of Giants</p>
                            <p class="light center">
                                Every public vehicle can be tracked and managed by Falcon to ensure smooth movement and prevent accidents, saving lives, time, and costs. 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="col s9">
            <div class="heading">
                Create a new network of stations
            </div>
            <%- include map.ejs %>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col s12">
                    <div class="row">
                        <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light button-right" type="submit" onclick="submitStations()">Submit
                        <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="card-panel light-grey ligthen-3">
                        Instructions:
                        <ol>
                            <li>Click on the position where you want to place a station</li>
                            <li>Enter the station name</li>
                            <li>Enter a short station code</li>
                            <li>Repeat the process as required, and click the <i>Submit</i> button when done</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include footer.ejs %>
</body>
</html>